---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — VANTA" description="The story behind VANTA men's streetwear.">
  <section class="bg-ink text-paper">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 py-24">
      <p class="font-display uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs text-acid mb-6">Our story</p>
      <h1 class="font-display uppercase font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-none">
        Weight you<br />can feel.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-20 space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
    <p>
      VANTA started with one frustration: men's basics that felt like paper and fell apart after
      a few washes. We wanted the opposite — pieces with weight, structure and a fit that gets
      better the more you wear them.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every tee starts at 240gsm. Hoodies are brushed-back and built oversized. Our suits are cut
      unstructured so you can throw a hoodie underneath and still look sharp. Nothing here is
      fast fashion — it's made to be kept.
    </p>
    <p>
      We design in small drops, produce in limited runs, and ship worldwide. No middlemen, no
      bloated retail markup — just heavyweight menswear, direct to you.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-ink/10">
      <div>
        <div class="font-display font-black text-4xl">240+</div>
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40 mt-1">gsm cotton</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-display font-black text-4xl">14d</div>
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40 mt-1">easy exchange</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-display font-black text-4xl">∞</div>
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40 mt-1">worldwide ship</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="font-display uppercase tracking-widest text-sm bg-ink text-paper px-8 py-4 inline-block hover:bg-ink/80 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
